              },
              "displayName": "Zhijie Shen",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "With the discovery service, the collector doesn't need to bind a configured port. And in the future, in a single app-level collector mode, we can't configure all collectors on one host to bind the same port. Therefore, I create patch to make the collector randomly bind an available port.  I add a test case to verify a good port is picked randomly. Also, I've verified that the distributed shell is working properly.",
